          a.btn.red(href='#') How to apply
      
      section.course-container
        article.row
          .large-6.medium-6.columns
            h2.course-heading 
              em BSc 
              | Finance and Business Management
            p Explore finance specialisms and core areas of business management, such as strategy, marketing and international business in this 3 year course. The strong emphasis on international will prepare you to face the challenges of global business. This course offers an excellent grounding for a career in accountancy and finance, but the broader business management knowledge you'll develop will also prepare you for a range of other roles in business and other sectors. Over 90% of our graduates are in employment or further study within 6 months of graduating.
            a.btn.red(href='#') How to apply
            a.btn.grey(href='http://www.reading.edu.my/learn/bsc-finance-and-business-management') Find out more
